arStrings.szText: The voice of the people. Beloved by the faithful of Zakarum. A favorite of the Que-Hegan. When Mephisto corrupted the church, Alia was the first to take up his banner.
She led a column of monks into Kurast and massacred the city. My grandfather would tell stories of an angel with a bloody knife, smiling as if the whole world was watching.
She was killed by a scared child with a rusty spear.
